public class ASNComplexNode
extends ASNRoleNode

This node type corresponds to the 'complex' products found within the decomposition. Logically it would thus indicate the need to assemble some simple components into a big one. Currently its a subclass of the main ASNRoleNode class so that it all gets seen by coordination fit etc
